    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="s03.2.6" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Engine Oil Temperature (EOT) Sensor</title>
        <figure id="f3450003009" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figJ09/J09014.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="192px" box="no"/>
            <caption>EOT sensor</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>The EOT sensor is a thermistor sensor. The ECM monitors the EOT signal and uses this information for the
            instrument panel oil temperature gauge. The EOT sensor is installed in the oil filter base assembly located
            on top of the engine.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
